{"tid":2360100,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"長頭髮應該留咩髮型好","createTime":"2021-01-09T12:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T14:06:32.000Z","uid":300420,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aff94f07f1cf54b26f3c8e1a6508544173a73d61","tid":2360100,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T12:11:48.000Z","msg":"自從完sem之後個人精神狀態好咗<br />\n身體恢復緊 啲頭髮都開始濃密返<br />\n而家個髮型睇落就好似咁樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyHNuqy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyHNuqy.png&h=a4f2f015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個冬菇頭咁(幅相冇畫到塊蔭) 個頭自動分界<br />\n但係側邊有兩隻角突咗出嚟 目前仲未垂到落去<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊諗住去剪頭髮 但係因為未試過留到咁長所以唔知要剪咩髮型好<br />\n<br />\n想剪個睇落去瀟灑啲 青春啲嘅髮型<br />\n有冇建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdda06ba9f2ee6344aaa0e7afcfa4619c593b29","tid":2360100,"uid":29929,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T12:13:11.000Z","msg":"你剪個free rider 會留既頭囉<br />\n垃圾free rider"},{"pid":"6bd4089a39a5f7eb9a0c1e1bf3f68cea975b1af9","tid":2360100,"uid":373951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1bdda06ba9f2ee6344aaa0e7afcfa4619c593b29","tid":2360100,"uid":29929,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T12:13:11.000Z","msg":"你剪個free rider 會留既頭囉<br />\n垃圾free rider"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T12:13:22.000Z","msg":"秒回"},{"pid":"346ba714f368c60ceff1ea3837f7e7cfab235c15","tid":2360100,"uid":300420,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bdda06ba9f2ee6344aaa0e7afcfa4619c593b29","tid":2360100,"uid":29929,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T12:13:11.000Z","msg":"你剪個free rider 會留既頭囉<br />\n垃圾free rider"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T12:15:07.000Z","msg":"勿引戰 講呢啲要有證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我已經學識忽視人身攻擊<br />\n閑話終日有 不理自然無<img src=\"/assets/